<section class="hero-small">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Newsletter</h1>
    <p class="lead">Stay informed with the latest pickleball news and insights</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About Our Newsletter</h2>
    <p>Our newsletter brings together the best content from across the pickleball world. We aggregate news from multiple trusted sources to provide you with a comprehensive view of what's happening in the sport.</p>
    
    <h3>What You'll Get</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Curated News:</strong> The most important stories from top pickleball publications</li>
      <li><strong>Tournament Updates:</strong> Coverage of major tournaments and player rankings</li>
      <li><strong>Training Tips:</strong> Expert advice to improve your game</li>
      <li><strong>Community Events:</strong> Local and international pickleball gatherings</li>
      <li><strong>Equipment Reviews:</strong> The latest gear and equipment recommendations</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Subscribe via RSS</h3>
    <p>Stay updated by subscribing to our RSS feed. You'll get instant notifications whenever new content is aggregated.</p>
    
    <div class="cta">
      <a href="/rss.xml" class="button">Subscribe to RSS Feed</a>
    </div>

    <h3>Recent Updates</h3>
    {% if collections.aggregatedItems.length > 0 %}
      <div class="items-list">
        {% for item in collections.aggregatedItems.slice(0, 5) %}
          <article class="item-row">
            <h4><a href="{{ item.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ item.title }}</a></h4>
            <p class="meta">
              <span class="source">{{ item.source }}</span> â€¢ 
              <span class="date">{{ item.pubDate | date("%B %d, %Y") }}</span>
            </p>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
